# Deployment Guide

This document summarizes the recommended production setups for CCFrame and the most important configuration knobs.

## Quick Start (install script)

```bash
curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lonelyrower/CCFrame/main/install.sh | bash
```

The script installs system dependencies (Node.js 20, PostgreSQL, Redis, PM2, Nginx), clones the repository, runs Prisma migrations, creates the initial admin user, and configures process supervisors. After installation you will see:

- Application URL and admin console URL
- Bootstrap admin account
- Location of the cloned project (`/var/www/ccframe` by default)

### Manual post-install steps

1. Copy `config/production.env.example` to `config/production.env` and fill in real credentials.
2. Restart the service so PM2 picks up the new environment file:
   ```bash
   cd /var/www/ccframe
   pm2 restart ccframe --update-env
   ```

## Configuration reference

All deployment targets (PM2, Docker, Railway, …) share the same environment variables. The table below lists the most common ones. A complete template lives in `config/production.env.example`.

| Variable | Description | Required | Default |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `DATABASE_URL` | PostgreSQL connection string | Yes | – |
| `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` | Random 32+ character secret used by NextAuth | Yes | – |
| `NEXTAUTH_URL` | Public URL of the deployment | Yes | – |
| `ADMIN_EMAIL` / `ADMIN_PASSWORD` | Initial admin account | Yes | – |
| `REDIS_URL` | Redis endpoint used by queues and caching | Recommended | `redis://redis:6379` |
| `STORAGE_PROVIDER` | `s3` or `local` | No | `local` |
| `S3_BUCKET_NAME`, `S3_REGION`, `S3_ENDPOINT`, `S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID`, `S3_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY` | S3 compatible storage settings | When using S3 | – |
| `CDN_BASE_URL` | Optional CDN domain prefix for images | No | – |
| `RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED` | Enable API rate limiting | No | `true` |
| `CACHE_TTL` / `IMAGE_CACHE_TTL` | Application level cache TTL (seconds) | No | `3600` / `31536000` |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | Pino logger level | No | `info` |

> Docker/PM2 deployments read environment variables from `config/production.env`. Local development still uses `.env` in the project root.

### Observability & metrics

- Prometheus metrics are available at `GET /api/metrics` (prefixed with `ccframe_`).
- Upload flow, semantic search, health checks, and queue processing include dedicated counters and histograms.
- Logs are emitted in JSON (Pino). Use `pm2 logs ccframe` or pipe to a log shipper such as Fluent Bit.

## Deployment options

### PM2 (bare metal / VPS)

```bash
cd /var/www/ccframe
git pull
npm install --production
npx prisma migrate deploy
npm run build
pm2 restart ccframe --update-env
```

Useful PM2 commands:

```bash
pm2 status
pm2 logs ccframe --lines 100
pm2 restart ccframe
pm2 reload ccframe
```

### Docker Compose

```bash
cp .env.docker.example .env    # adjust credentials
mkdir -p config
cp config/production.env.example config/production.env  # edit values
# ensure uploads/ is writable if STORAGE_PROVIDER=local

docker compose up -d --build
```

The compose stack contains Next.js (web), BullMQ worker, PostgreSQL, Redis, MinIO and Nginx. On start-up the `web` and `worker` services run `prisma migrate deploy` and `prisma generate` automatically before launching the app.

### Manual deployment

```bash
git clone https://github.com/lonelyrower/CCFrame.git
cd CCFrame
npm install
cp .env.example .env  # edit values
npx prisma migrate deploy
npm run build
npm start
```

## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Possible cause | Suggested fix |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `/api/metrics` returns 404 | Route not deployed or build cache stale | Ensure the app has been rebuilt after upgrading (`npm run build && pm2 restart ccframe`). |
| Login或上传接口返回 429 | 触发速率限制 | 检查 `RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED` 设置并查看 `/api/metrics` 中 `ccframe_upload_events_total`/`auth_rate_limited` 指标；如需阶段性放宽可上调 Redis 配置或关闭限流（仅限内网环境）。 |
| 上传预签名成功但处理队列无响应 | Worker 服务未运行或 Redis 不可用 | `pm2 status` 检查 `ccframe-worker` 或 `docker compose logs worker`，确认 `REDIS_URL` 正确。 |
| MinIO/S3 连接失败 | 凭据错误或网络不可达 | 访问 `/api/health` 观察 `storage` 状态及错误信息，核对 `S3_ENDPOINT`、`S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID/SECRET`。 |
| Prisma migration 报错 | 数据库连接失败或 schema 变更冲突 | 执行 `npx prisma migrate deploy --preview-feature` 查看详细日志，确认 `DATABASE_URL` 与数据库权限。

备份 & 恢复 PostgreSQL：

```bash
pg_dump -h localhost -U gallery_user ccframe > backup.sql
psql -h localhost -U gallery_user ccframe < backup.sql
```

常用日志位置：

- 应用：`pm2 logs ccframe`
- Nginx：`/var/log/nginx/error.log`
- Docker：`docker compose logs web`

遵循最小权限原则，定期轮换管理员密码，并建议在入口层启用 HTTPS/防火墙限制。
